      <title>孟加拉国将预算赤字目标削减至 2015 年以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/bangladesh-slashes-budget-deficit-target-to-lowest-since-2015</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在外汇储备持续减少的情况下，由于总理谢赫·哈西娜领导的政府放缓支出并提高税收，孟加拉国计划将预算赤字削减至十多年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/bangladesh-slashes-budget-deficit-target-to-lowest-since-2015</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 09:24:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
